data.description: Priced to Sell!!!!Welcome to your dream retirement haven in beautiful Naples, Florida. Nestled within a vibrant 55 and older boating community, this charming manufactured home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious floor plan with your comfort in mind. With ample windows throughout, natural light brightens the area creating warm and inviting abundance. The community boat ramp will bring you to the gulf in a short 20 minute cruise. This community offers extremely low HOA fees and YOU OWN THE LAND. Located in the heart of South Naples, you'll have easy access to stunning beaches, world class golf courses, shopping, and both casual and upscale dining from both Naples and Marco Island. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to embrace the best of retirement living in a welcoming 55 and older community. Schedule your showing today.
